%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20unjammable%20drones%20are%20causing%20chaos.%20A%20tech%20firm%20says%20it%20has%20a%20fix%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20fight%20back.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223346%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20fiber-optic%20drone%20is%20seen%20during%20a%20test%20flight%20in%20the%20Kyiv%20region%20in%20December%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677da97a50dfd88e193d5a59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222231%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20fiber-optic%20drone%20is%20seen%20during%20a%20test%20flight%20in%20the%20Kyiv%20region%20in%20December%202024.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Viktor%20Fridshon%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20explosive-packed%20drones%20modified%20with%20fiber-optic%20cables.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20drones%20are%20dangerous%2C%20as%20they%20can't%20be%20jammed%20with%20electronic%20warfare%20and%20are%20harder%20to%20detect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20one%20Ukrainian%20company%20is%20developing%20a%20solution%20so%20front-line%20soldiers%20can%20find%20the%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20forces%20are%20using%20explosive-packed%20drones%20connected%20to%20their%20operators%20by%20fiber-optic%20cables%20to%20deliver%20unjammable%20precision%20strikes%20on%20Ukrainian%20troops%20and%20military%20equipment%2C%20and%20Kyiv%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20fix%20to%20fight%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiber-optic%20drones%20have%20been%20increasingly%20appearing%20in%20combat%20over%20about%20the%20last%20year%2C%20and%20they're%20a%20challenge.%20These%20drones%20are%20dangerous%20because%20they%20can't%20be%20jammed%20with%20traditional%20electronic%20warfare%20and%20are%20difficult%20to%20defend%20against%2C%20highlighting%20the%20need%20for%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drones%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20real%20problem%26quot%3B%20because%20%26quot%3Bwe%20cannot%20detect%20and%20intercept%20them%26quot%3B%20electronically%2C%20Yuriy%2C%20a%20major%20in%20an%20electronic-warfare%20unit%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20National%20Guard%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20see%2C%20we%20can%20fight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20one%20that%20the%20defense%20industry%20is%20looking%20into%20closely.%20Kara%20Dag%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20an%20American-Ukrainian%20technology%20company%20that's%20developing%20software%20and%20hardware%20to%20defend%20against%20Russian%20drones%20for%20the%20military%20and%20working%20on%20a%20solution%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20pseudonym%20John%20for%20security%20purposes%2C%20said%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bwar%20of%20drones.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20BI%20Ukraine%20had%20managed%20this%20fight%20well%20with%20jamming%20techniques%2C%20but%20Russia%20has%20found%20ways%20to%20slip%20past%20some%20of%20its%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiber-optic%20drones%2C%20which%20Russia%20appears%20to%20have%20started%20flying%20into%20battle%20last%20spring%2C%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-isnt-ready-drones-potential-biggest-threat-next-battlefield-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst-person%20view%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20FPV%2C%20drones%2C%20but%20rather%20than%20rely%20on%20a%20signal%20connection%2C%20they%20are%20wired%20with%20cables%20that%20preserve%20a%20stable%20connection.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20these%20drones%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-fiber-optic-unjammable-drones-fix-a-big-problem-war-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresistant%20to%20electronic%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20radio%20frequency%20jammers%2C%20and%20produce%20high-quality%20video%20transmissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222453%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Russian%20soldier%20launches%20an%20FPV%20drone%20at%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20November%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677d8da52be30c194fc542be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221636%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Russian%20soldier%20launches%20an%20FPV%20drone%20at%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20November%202024.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20combat%20footage%20from%20Russian%20fiber-optic%20drones%20began%20to%20circulate%2C%20indicating%20a%20more%20lasting%20presence%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20Now%2C%20both%20militaries%20are%20using%20these%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiber-optic%20drones%20are%20highly%20dangerous%2C%20John%20said%2C%20as%20they%20can%20fly%20in%20tunnels%2C%20close%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20through%20valleys%2C%20and%20in%20other%20areas%20where%20other%20drones%20might%20lose%20connection%20with%20their%20operators.%20They%20are%20also%20tough%20to%20detect%20because%20they%20don't%20emit%20any%20radio%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20can%20use%20these%20drones%20to%20destroy%20Ukrainian%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20study%20its%20defensive%20positions%2C%20he%20said.%20Since%20they%20don't%20have%20bandwidth%20problems%2C%20these%20drones%20%26quot%3Bcan%20transmit%20very%20high-quality%20picture%20and%20they%20literally%20see%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drones%20aren't%20without%20their%20disadvantages%2C%20though.%20Yuriy%20shared%20that%20the%20fiber-optic%20drones%20are%20slower%20than%20the%20untethered%20FPV%20drones%20and%20unable%20to%20make%20sharp%20changes%20in%20direction.%20He%20said%20that%20Russia%20does%20not%20have%20too%20many%20of%20these%20drones%2C%20either%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20use%20them%20in%20every%20direction%20of%20the%20front%20lines.%20But%20where%20they%20are%20