al%20stock-market%20correction%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20is%20heating%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20down%20just%205%25%20from%20its%20record%20high%20reached%20on%20December%206%2C%20concerns%20are%20brewing%20that%20volatility%20is%20set%20to%20surge%20this%20year%20due%20to%20a%20new%20President%20in%20the%20White%20House%20and%20historical%20data%20that%20suggests%20the%20current%20rally%20is%20getting%20long%20in%20the%20tooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20can%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20its%20own%20success.%20After%20two%20strong%20years%20in%202023%20and%202024%2C%20risk%20increases%20for%20an%20uninspiring%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephen%20Suttmeier%2C%20technical%20strategist%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuttmeier%20highlighted%20that%20the%20average%20and%20median%20return%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20during%20the%20third%20year%20of%20a%20new%20bull%20market%20is%205%25%2C%20well%20below%20the%20average%20annual%20return%20of%20about%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20major%20stock%20market%20averages%20are%20down%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20percentage%20points%20from%20their%20December%20highs%2C%20the%20internals%20show%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20suffered%20a%20lot%20of%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20technical%20cracks%20have%20recently%20emerged%2C%26quot%3B%20Adan%20Turnquist%2C%20chief%20technical%20strategist%20at%20LPL%20Financial%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BMomentum%20in%20stocks%20has%20recently%20stalled%20as%20the%20calendar%20turned%20to%202025%2C%20while%20deteriorating%20breadth%20measures%20are%20flashing%20potential%20warning%20signs%20for%20a%20deeper%20pullback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20of%20the%20eleven%20stock%20market%20sectors%20are%20trading%20above%20their%20200-day%20moving%20average%2C%20down%20from%20all%20eleven%20in%20late%20December.%20Another%20measure%20of%20market%20breadth%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stocks%20above%20their%20200-day%20moving%20average%2C%20also%20decline%20sharply%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20from%20about%2076%25%20to%2055%25%20on%20Wedensday%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20StockCharts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20200-day%20moving%20average%20is%20a%20closely%20watched%20technical%20indicator%20that%20helps%20identify%20the%20long-term%20direction%20of%20a%20trend.%20When%20securities%20fall%20below%20their%20200-day%20moving%20average%2C%20it%20sends%20a%20warning%20sign%20to%20traders%20that%20the%20prior%20uptrend%20in%20a%20stock%20price%20could%20be%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20turning%20into%20a%20down%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20concerns%20growing%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-2025-outlook-us-debt-levels-deficit-ruchir-sharma-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20experience%20an%20imminent%20sell-off%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20three%20equity%20strategists%20to%20better%20gauge%20how%20painful%20a%20potential%20stock%20decline%20could%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20they%20had%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffd1e63a-40f8-463b-b98a-b583b7c3edba%5C%22%3E13%25%20correction%20%E2%80%94%20Fairlead%20Strategies%20(Will%20Tamplin)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Tamplin%2C%20senior%20analyst%20at%20technical%20analysis%20research%20firm%20Fairlead%20Strategies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20rising%20200-day%20moving%20average%20is%20a%20logical%20level%20of%20support%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20technical%20level%20is%20at%20about%205%2C570.%20If%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20tests%20that%20level%20and%20breaks%20below%20it%20decisively%2C%20the%20next%20area%20of%20support%20for%20the%20index%20is%20the%2038.2%25%20Fibonacci%20retracement%20level%20at%205%2C337.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decline%20to%20that%20level%20would%20represent%20potential%20downside%20of%2010%25%20from%20current%20levels%20and%20a%20peak%20to%20trough%20decline%20of%20about%2013%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22397324c1-2b36-4c8b-82c2-291f8937eab4%5C%22%3E15%25%20correction%20%E2%80%94%20Baird%20(Ross%20Mayfield)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20Mayfield%2C%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Baird%2C%20is%20bullish%20on%20the%20stock%20market%20for%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20bullish%20view%20doesn't%20negate%20the%20view%20that%20a%20stock%20market%20correction%20could%20be%20near%2C%20Mayfield%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20arguing%20that%20after%20a%20strong%20two-year%20rally%2C%20a%20painful%20decline%20is%20overdue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20average%20a%20correction%20roughly%20once%20every%20two%20years%2C%20but%20we%20rarely%20see%20a%20bear%20market%20without%20an%20associated%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayfield%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%202025%20base%20case%20is%20for%20a%20continued%20economic%20expansion%20(i.e.%2C%20no%20recession)%20and%20stock%20market%20gains%20across%20the%20full%20year%2C%20but%20a%20double%20digit%20pullback%20(ala%20early%202018)%20would%20be%20right%20in%20line%20with%20historical%20average%20and%20wouldn't%20be%20surprising%20given%20the%20headwinds%20facing%20markets%20and%20extended%20valuations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMayfield%20said%20a%20downturn%20of%20as%20much%20as%2015%25%20is%20feasible%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2b67615-8d7a-45ff-9274-2b66a6c13bde%5C%22%3E16%25%20correction%20%E2%80%94%20CFRA%20Research%20(Sam%20Stovall)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year%20has%20started%20off%20on%20the%20wrong%20foot%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Stovall%2C%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20CFRA%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStovall%20observed%20that%20the%20Santa%20Claus%20Rally%2C%20which%20occurs%20during%20the%20last%20five%20trading%20days%20of%20the%20old%20year%20and%20the%20first%20two%20of%20the%20new%2C%20didn't%20deliver%2C%20which%20is%20historically%20a%20bad%20omen%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Santa%20should%20fail%20to%20call%2C%20bears%20may%20come%20to%20Broad%20and%20Wall%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20old%20Wall%20Street%20adage%20goes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Stovall%2C%20a%20key%20technical%20Fibonacci%20level%2C%205%2C130%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20start%20of%20the%20current%20bull%20market%20on%20October%2012%2C%202022%2C%20is%20crucial%20for%20investors%20to%20watch%20as%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decline%20to%20that%20level%20would%20represent%20a%20peak-to-trough%20decline%20of%2016%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20experienced%20a%20decline%20of%2016%25%20or%20more%20was%20in%202022%2C%20during%20a%20brutal%20bear%20market%20that%20was%20sparked%20by%20surging%20bond%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20bond%20markets%20recently%20throwing%20a%20tantrum%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbond-yields-interest-rates-donald-trump-stock-market-liz-truss-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10-year%20US%20Treasury%20yield%20approaches%205%25%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20investors%20could%20once%20again%20be%20worried%20that%20the%20money-losing%20environment%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbond-yields-interest-rates-donald-trump-inflation-tax-cuts-tariffs-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20could%20return%20this%20year.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-correction-outlook-painful-sell-off-predictions-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736598901000%2C%22visua