f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-ultra-processed-foods-may-be-healthier-than-homemade-scientist-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20is%20it%20about%20ultra-processed%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20seems%20to%20drive%20over-consumption%20and%20weight%20gain%3F%26quot%3B%20metabolism%20researcher%20Kevin%20Hall%20recently%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20works%20at%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%2C%20where%20he%20is%20conducting%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-making-ultra-processed-foods-healthier-in-major-new-study-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunusual%20experiment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20brings%20people%20into%20a%20tightly%20controlled%20food%20lab%20for%20one%20month%2C%20and%20tests%20out%20how%20four%20different%20diets%20%E2%80%94%20one%20unprocessed%2C%20and%20three%20ultra-processed%2C%20but%20all%20with%20the%20same%20levels%20of%20key%20nutrients%20%E2%80%94%20impact%20people's%20hunger%2C%20fullness%2C%20calorie%20consumption%2C%20weight%20gain%2C%20and%20fat%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20study%20is%20still%20ongoing%2C%20he's%20been%20sharing%20some%20initial%20results%20with%20colleagues%20in%20the%20US%20and%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20findings%20offer%20some%20hints%20about%20why%20UPFs%20can%20not%20only%20lead%20to%20weight%20gain%20but%20also%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20dump%20fat.%20The%20study%20is%20also%20showing%20that%20simple%20tweaks%20could%20make%20a%20huge%20difference.%20Perhaps%2C%20Hall%20says%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-a-completely-unprocessed-food-diet-benefits-drawbacks-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20out%20ultra-processed%3C%2Fa%3E%20products%20to%20have%20a%20satisfying%2C%20relatively%20healthy%20plate%20of%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a9bfc8f-3a29-4e7b-8e67-a28db64c42b6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20an%20ultra-processed%20diet%2C%20patients%20gained%202%20lbs%20a%20week%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22382%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meal%20with%20sandwiches%2C%20lemonade%2C%20chips%2C%20and%20dip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678193d08951662c9f1fb641%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22313%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20example%20of%20an%20ultra-processed%20meal%20from%20Hall's%20original%202019%20study.%20In%20the%20new%20study%2C%20there%20are%20fewer%20ultra-processed%20drinks%2C%20with%20more%20nutrients%20like%20fiber%20being%20put%20directly%20into%20the%20foods%20offered.%3Cp%3ENIH%2C%20NIDDK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hall's%20patients%20switched%20diets%2C%20their%20calorie%20intake%20shifted%20dramatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20week%20of%20unprocessed%20meals%2C%20full%20of%20fresh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-aging-foods-brain-heart-health-better-immunity-longevity-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetables%2C%20beans%2C%20legumes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20whole%20grains%2C%20participants%20ate%20an%20average%20of%202%2C700%20calories%20per%20day.%20They%20also%20tended%20to%20lose%20a%20little%20weight%2C%20about%20a%20pound%20of%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20changed%20when%20they%20switched%20to%20an%2080%25%20ultra-processed%20diet.%20Same%20amount%20of%20food%20offered%2C%20same%20levels%20of%20sugar%2C%20salt%2C%20fat%2C%20carbs%2C%20protein%2C%20and%20fiber%20on%20the%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20patients%20ended%20up%20consuming%20more%20food%20to%20achieve%20the%20same%20level%20of%20fullness%20%E2%80%94%20ingesting%20about%203%2C700%20calories%20per%20day%20on%20average.%20On%20ultra-processed%20foods%2C%20the%20patients'%20weight%20shot%20up%20by%20over%20two%20pounds%20in%20a%20single%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22382%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22broccoli%2C%20salad%2C%20apples%2C%20bulgur%2C%20meat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6781943a8951662c9f1fb64f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20example%20of%20an%20unprocessed%20meal%20from%20Hall's%202019%20study.%3Cp%3ENIH%2C%20NIDDK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%2C%20while%20still%20preliminary%2C%20are%20even%20more%20striking%20than%20the%20last%20experiment%20Hall%20did%20like%20this%2C%20when%20patients%20ate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-processed-foods-lead-to-weight-gain-nih-study-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E500%20extra%20calories%20per%20day%20on%20ultra-processed%20diets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20might%20not%20even%20feel%20like%20they're%20eating%20more%20when%20they%20consume%20those%20ultra-processed%20meals.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20each%20bite%20of%20ultra-processed%20food%20is%20far%20more%20calorie-dense%20than%20a%20homemade%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22079b9b16-34ff-44db-bc6f-5f7046b70067%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdding%20moisture%20made%20ultra-processed%20meals%20'healthier'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22795%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20cutting%20vegetables%20at%20NIH%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666bb962e07904901818fee7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chef%20at%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health's%20metabolic%20kitchen.%20The%20NIH%20precisely%20measures%20the%20amount%20of%20key%20nutrients%20that%20are%20available%20in%20each%20meal%2C%20matching%20ultra-processed%20to%20unprocessed%20offerings.%20But%20it's%20up%20to%20participants%20to%20decide%20what%20they%20want%20to%20eat%2C%20and%20how%20much.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Rymaruk%2C%20NIDDK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECutting%20out%20ultra-processed%20foods%20isn't%20realistic%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Hall%20said.%20But%20what%20if%20you%20could%20make%20a%20Western%20diet%20less%20bad%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoping%20to%20reduce%20people's%20weight%20gain%20and%20improve%20satiety%20with%20fewer%20calories%2C%20Hall%20(and%20his%20team%20of%20clinical%20chefs)%20devised%20two%20new%20diets%20to%20test%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20diets%20were%2080%25%20ultra-processed%20but%20with%20some%20crucial%20adjustments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20new%20diet%2C%20researchers%20lowered%20the%20amount%20of%20what%20are%20called%20%26quot%3Bhyper-palatable%20foods%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20foods%20that%20combine%20sugar%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20fat%20in%20ways%20that%20aren't%20typically%20seen%20in%20nature%20(think%3A%20rich%2C%20salty%20ice%20cream%2C%20a%20donut%2C%20or%20veggies%20in%20cream%20sauce).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20eating%20burger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675a0df9dc8b666017f29be7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeyper-palatable%20foods%20combine%20fat%2C%20sodium%2C%20and%20sugar%20in%20unnatural%20ways.%3Cp%3Ed3sign%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAddiction%20researcher%20Tera%20Fazzino%20coined%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bhyper-palatable%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20way%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20the%20irresistibility%20of%20junk%20food.%20She%20hypothesizes%20that%20hyper-palatable%20ultra-processed%20foods%20might%20mess%20with%20our%20minds%2C%20and%20drive%20people%20to%20eat%20more%20than%20they%20would%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20didn't%20ring%20true%20in%20Hall's%20new%20study.%20The%20patients%20who%20cut%20out%20hyper-palatable%20foods%20only%20saved%20themselves%20200%20calories%20a%20day%2C%20and%20gained%20over%201%20lb%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20diet%2C%20the%20chefs%20lowered%20the%20amount%20of%20hyper