0we%20decided%20to%20look%20at%20the%20body%20composition%20changes%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a10387c-8cc2-41d1-bff4-d3fb42757041%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20nut%20we%20haven't%20cracked%3A%20Achieving%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20weight-loss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22person%20stepping%20on%20scale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6781977450dfd88e193df06a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223194%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENot%20all%20weight%20loss%20is%20created%20equal.%3Cp%3EimageBROKER%2FMaren%20Winter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20people%20on%20the%20100%25%20unprocessed%20diet%20lost%20body%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%26quot%3Bhealthier%26quot%3B%20ultra-processed%20diet%2C%20people%20lost%20about%20a%20pound%20of%20weight%20in%20a%20week%2C%20but%20it%20was%20coming%20from%20fat-free%20mass.%20That%20means%20muscle%2C%20bone%2C%20tissue%2C%20or%20maybe%20just%20water%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20is%20not%20yet%20sure%20why%20this%20is%20happening%2C%20but%20he%20says%20it%20could%20have%20to%20do%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bdigestability%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20ultra-processed%20foods%20%E2%80%94%20in%20other%20words%2C%20how%20they%20are%20handled%20inside%20our%20bodies%2C%20compared%20to%20whole%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20learn%20what%20those%20mechanisms%20are%2C%20then%20the%20really%20smart%20people%20who%20are%20ingenious%20food%20technologists%20and%20scientists%20can%20maybe%20re-engineer%20some%20of%20these%20foods%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20many%20narratives%20and%20hypotheses%20that%20sound%20reasonable%2C%20but%20until%20you%20actually%20do%20the%20studies%20to%20test%20that%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b03729c-23c8-443c-97e6-845b5425f90b%5C%22