20sometimes%20that%20means%20everyone%20is%20doing%20different%20things%20in%20different%20places.%20I%20never%20anticipated%20how%20little%20I%20would%20see%20my%20husband%20once%20our%20third%20was%20born.%20But%20once%20she%20was%20here%2C%20I%20finally%20understood%20how%20parents%20can%20say%20they%20start%20to%20feel%20more%20like%20roommates%20rather%20than%20a%20couple.%20Three%20children%20mean%20three%20different%20sets%20of%20appointments%2C%20extracurriculars%2C%20bathtimes%2C%20and%20bedtimes.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20to%20make%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshared-google-calendar-key-successful-marriage-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschedule%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20talk%2C%20let%20alone%20hang%20out%20without%20an%20offspring%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f062417f-974e-4f39-8c53-3d572e5d34cb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20the%20perfect%20mom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20wish%20someone%20told%20me%20mom-perfection%20is%20pointless%20when%20I%20was%20pregnant%20the%20first%20time%20around.%20Perhaps%20it%20would%20have%20spared%20me%20the%20silly%20thought%20that%20I%20could%20try%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20it%20right%26quot%3B%20with%20my%20third.%20The%20truth%20is%20the%20best%20moms%20don't%20get%20it%20right.%20Mistakes%20are%20normal%20when%20you're%20a%20parent.%20If%20you%20set%20the%20bar%20too%20high%20with%20unattainable%20goals%20and%20expectations%2C%20you'll%20ultimately%20feel%20horrible%20every%20time%20you%20don't%20meet%20them.%20Instead%20of%20being%20perfect%2C%20just%20be%20regular%20%E2%80%94%20be%20loving%2C%20be%20funny%2C%20show%20your%20kids%20you're%20human%20with%20real%20feelings%20and%20admit%20that%20you%20sometimes%20make%20mistakes.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%20don't%20give%20up%2C%20you'll%20be%20the%20best%20mom%20no%20matter%20what.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c44efcd4-c9aa-41e4-a191-c056ae35e829%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELower%20your%20expectations%2C%20then%20lower%20them%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20had%20just%20one%20or%20two%20kids%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20be%20on%20time%20for%20parties%20with%20a%20perfectly%20wrapped%20gift%20or%20warm%20delicious%20appetizer%20in%20hand.%20My%20girls%20were%20by%20my%20side%2C%20dressed%20in%20clean%20clothes%20with%20matching%20socks%20and%20a%20bow.%20Nowadays%2C%20I%20am%20lucky%20if%20I%20remember%20to%20change%20out%20of%20my%20slippers%20before%20I%20leave%20the%20house.%20And%20you%20know%20what%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20fine.%20You%20get%20used%20to%20things%20not%20being%20exactly%20how%20you%20used%20to%20like%20them%20and%20learn%20quickly%20that%20having%20low%20expectations%20is%20the%20way%20to%20live.%20After%20all%2C%20having%20low%20expectations%20isn't%20such%20a%20bad%20thing.%20Your%20family%20and%20friends%20will%20forgive%20you%20for%20being%20late%20and%20accept%20the%20chaos%20(as%20they're%20probably%20in%20a%20state%20of%20chaos%20on%20their%20own).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e7598dd-9169-4fbd-a135-73b4c0dcf340%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20heart%20may%20feel%20like%20it's%20going%20to%20explode%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20talking%20from%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20referring%20to%20the%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20love%2C%20pride%2C%20and%20joy%20you%20will%20experience%20when%20you%20see%20your%20three%20children%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20recall%20when%20I%20had%20the%20epiphany%20that%20having%20a%20third%20child%20is%20worth%20every%20challenge%20and%20bump%20in%20the%20road%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20happened.%20One%20day%20I%20looked%20around%20and%20knew%20I%20was%20right%20where%20I%20am%20supposed%20to%20be.%20Even%20though%20you%20feel%20three%20times%20as%20exhausted%20and%20three%20times%20as%20busy%20when%20you%20have%20your%20third%20child%2C%20you%20will%20also%20undoubtedly%20feel%20three%20times%20in%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-third-child-kid-can-change-family-unexpected-ways-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736593021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678130b288b000981b4a5779%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-third-child-kid-can-change-family-unexpected-ways-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20contemplating%20a%20third%20child%2C%20know%20that%20experience%20means%20nothing.%20Here's%20what%20surprised%20me%20the%20most%20about%20adding%20one%20more%20to%20our%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Caitlin%20Houston)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-third-child-kid-can-change-family-unexpected-ways-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Walgreens%20CEO%20says%20stopping%20shoplifting%20is%20like%20a%20'hand-to-hand%20combat%20battle'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walgreens%20pharmacy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c571f9ceb3ce81c3364ed23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalgreens%20Boots%20Alliance%20CEO%20Tim%20Wentworth%20said%20minimizing%20shoplifting%20is%20an%20ongoing%20challenge.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWalgreens'%20CEO%20said%20the%20company%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Bcreative%26quot%3B%20steps%20to%20address%20shoplifting%20and%20shrink.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20anti-theft%20measures%20can%20be%20effective%2C%20they%20can%20also%20hurt%20a%20store's%20sales%2C%20CEO%20Tim%20Wentworth%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pharmacy%20chain%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%2