C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BCCI%20Calls%20Meeting%20With%20Gambhir%2C%20Says%20Report.%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20May%20Be%20Given...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20of%20leading%20batters%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20be%20discussed%20threadbare%20in%20a%20meeting%20that%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20with%20BCCI%20officials%20to%20review%20the%20recent%20tour%20to%20Australia%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20back-to-back%20series%20defeats%20against%20New%20Zealand%20(home)%20and%20Australia%20(away)%20and%20the%20diminishing%20returns%20with%20the%20bat%20have%20put%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20under%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20has%20learned%20that%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20will%20discuss%20in%20detail%20the%20future%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20to%20activate%20the%20transition%20switch%20from%20next%20month's%20Champions%20Trophy%20or%20wait%20for%20the%20cycle%20to%20end%20with%20the%20ICC%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it's%20likely%20that%20the%20senior%20batters%20will%20get%20another%20chance%20to%20redeem%20themselves%20at%20the%20ODI%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20a%20format%20in%20which%20they%20have%20always%20excelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20may%20also%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20fact%20that%20both%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20have%20played%20just%20three%20ODIs%20in%202024%20after%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%20and%20that%20could%20be%20too%20light%20a%20sample%20size%20to%20make%20a%20final%20call%20on%20their%2050-over%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20endured%20different%20fortunes%20too%20in%20the%20series%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kohli%20amassed%2024%2C%2014%20and%2020%20in%20Colombo%2C%20Rohit%20walked%20away%20with%20scores%20of%2058%2C%2064%20and%2035%20against%20the%20Lankans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20overall%2C%20Kohli%20has%20been%20a%20champion%20performer%20in%2050-overs%2C%20his%20staple%20format%20and%20a%20good%20outing%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20could%20bring%20him%2C%20and%20Rohit%20too%2C%20back%20into%20a%20good%20frame%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20Test%20future%20is%20different.%20The%20next%20assignment%20is%20an%20away%20five-match%20series%20against%20England%2C%20and%20the%20mandarins%20will%20certainly%20assess%20the%20drying%20runs%20from%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20in%20the%20traditional%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20recent%20outing%20against%20Australia%2C%20Kohli%2C%20despite%20a%20hundred%20at%20Perth%2C%20could%20garner%20only%20190%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2023.75%20while%20Rohit%2C%20who%20skipped%20the%20first%20Test%20and%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20fifth%20match%2C%20made%2031%20runs%20at%206.2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20performances%20will%20certainly%20be%20mooted%20thoroughly%20while%20seeking%20Gambhir's%20views%20on%20their%20desire%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20longest%20version%20of%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Gambhir-led%20coaching%20staff%20too%20could%20be%20assayed%2C%20and%20asked%20about%20their%20vision%20to%20handle%20the%20transition%20period%20without%20any%20more%20hiccups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChampions%20Trophy%20team%20selection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20review%20meeting%2C%20the%20selectors%2C%20led%20by%20Agarkar%2C%20will%20also%20convene%20on%20Saturday%20evening%20to%20pick%20the%20Indian%20squad%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20play%20all%20its%20matches%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20will%20open%20the%20campaign%20with%20a%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20February%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20team%20will%20be%20announced%20on%20this%20day%20itself%2C%20as%20the%20selectors%20have%20time%20till%20January%2012%20to%20release%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20assess%20the%20fitness%20level%20of%20star%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20who%20is%20recuperating%20from%20back%20spasms%2C%20and%20veteran%20fast%20bowler%20Mohammed%20Shami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%2C%20who%20has%20not%20played%20since%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20because%20of%20an%20ankle%20surgery%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20green%20signal%20from%20BCCI's%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20physics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20has%20played%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy%20and%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20matches%20recently%20for%20Bengal%20to%20underline%20his%20increasing%20fitness%20levels%20and%20match%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20interesting%20point%20will%20be%20to%20see%20whether%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20will%20get%20the%20nod%20after%20doing%20well%20in%2019%20Tests%20and%2023%20T20I%20since%20making%20his%20debut%20in%20mid-2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeam%20for%20England%20T20Is%2C%20ODIs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selectors%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20discuss%20and%20pick%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20five%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20against%20England%20for%20the%20home%20series%2C%20beginning%20from%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20not%20be%20many%20surprises%20as%20the%20team%20that%20did%20duty%20in%20South%20Africa%20late%20last%20year%20could%20be%20picked%20up%20again%20for%20the%20T20Is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20could%20be%20included%20in%20the%20ODIs%20depending%20on%20the%20fitness%20certificate%20from%20CoE%2C%20which%20is%20understood%20to%20be%20positive%20though%20it%20will%20be%20assessed%20deeply%20before%20taking%20a%20final%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20and%20fellow%20pacer%20Akash%20Deep%2C%20who%20will%20also%20be%20in%20CoE%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20recovery%20from%20a%20back%20niggle%2C%20will%20miss%20the%20white%20ball%20series%20against%20Engl