0envelops%20a%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pacific%20Palisades%2C%20a%20particularly%20hard-hit%20area%2C%20several%20hydrants%20reportedly%20failed%20or%20provided%20insufficient%20water.%20Similar%20issues%20arose%20in%20Altadena%20and%20Pasadena%2C%20where%20firefighters%20reported%20low%20water%20pressure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhvh261go_los-angeles-fire-hydrant-afp-_625x300_11_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pacific%20Palisades%2C%20the%20local%20water%20system%20relies%20on%20gravity-fed%20storage%20tanks%20situated%20in%20hilltop%20areas.%20These%20tanks%20-%20designed%20to%20hold%20about%20one%20million%20gallons%20each%20-%20supply%20water%20to%20hydrants%20below.%20However%2C%20the%20intense%20firefighting%20efforts%20drained%20the%20tanks%20rapidly%2C%20leading%20to%20dry%20hydrants%20in%20higher-elevation%20neighborhoods%20like%20Palisades%20Highlands.%20According%20to%20a%20DWP%20official%2C%20water%20demand%20surged%20to%20four%20times%20the%20usual%20rate%20for%2015%20hours%20straight%2C%20overwhelming%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompounding%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20nearby%20DWP%20reservoir%20was%20out%20of%20service%20for%20maintenance.%20Officials%20are%20now%20investigating%20how%20this%20may%20have%20further%20limited%20water%20availability.%20While%20tanker%20trucks%20were%20dispatched%20to%20supply%20water%20in%20critical%20areas%2C%20the%20logistical%20challenges%20of%20transporting%20water%20delayed%20efforts%20to%20address%20the%20shortages%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETopography%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20water%20distribution%20challenges.%20Los%20Angeles%20spans%20a%20range%20of%20elevations%2C%20from%20sea%20level%20to%20over%201%2C500%20feet%20in%20Pacific%20Palisades.%20Water%20systems%20in%20such%20areas%20are%20divided%20into%20pressure%20zones%2C%20typically%20in%20100-foot%20elevation%20increments.%20These%20zones%20can%20limit%20water%20flow%20when%20demand%20surges%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Altadena%20and%20Pasadena%2C%20water%20distribution%20faced%20additional%20complications.%20The%20Eaton%20Fire%2C%20which%20caused%20extensive%20damage%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20exposed%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20local%20water%20suppliers.%20These%20suppliers%20struggled%20to%20maintain%20adequate%20pressure%20due%20to%20power%20outages%20that%20affected%20their%20pumps.%20Power%20was%20cut%20in%20some%20areas%20to%20protect%20firefighters%20from%20falling%20power%20lines%20and%20cables.%20It%20was%20a%20Catch-22%20situation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Filcdr1rg_los-angeles-fire-afp-_625x300_11_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palisades%20Fire%20alone%20destroyed%20over%205%2C000%20structures%2C%20while%20the%20Eaton%20Fire%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20another%204%2C000%20to%205%2C000.%20The%20damage%20sustained%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20available%20to%20tackle%20to%20prevent%20that%20is%20grossly%20mismatched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20has%20ordered%20an%20independent%20investigation%20into%20the%20water%20supply%20failures%2C%20describing%20the%20reports%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20troubling.%26quot%3B%20The%20investigation%20will%20examine%20the%20preparedness%20and%20response%20of%20agencies%20like%20DWP%20and%20local%20utilities.%20Additionally%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20city%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mayor%20Karen%20Bass%2C%20have%20faced%20criticism%20over%20budget%20cuts%20to%20fire%20department%20resources%2C%20which%20some%20argue%20have%20weakened%20the%20city's%20ability%20to%20respond%20to%20large-scale%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20proposed%20various%20strategies%20to%20address%20these%20challenges.%20Expanding%20water%20storage%20capacity%20in%20high-risk%20areas%2C%20upgrading%20pipelines%20to%20handle%20higher%20demand%2C%20and%20investing%20in%20backup%20power%20systems%20for%20pumps%20are%20among%20the%20suggested%20measures.%20However%2C%20these%20solutions%20come%20with%20financial%20and%20logistical%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20firefighters%20have%20turned%20to%20unconventional%20water%20sources%2C%20such%20as%20swimming%20pools%20or%20ocean%20water%2C%20when%20hydrants%20fail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736574300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F542mu8d8_los-angeles-fire-afp-_625x300_11_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flos-angeles-wildfire-la-wildfire-california-wildfire-explained-why-hydrants-ran-dry-during-deadly-los-angeles-wildfires-7448282%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20crews%20battled%20devastating%20wildfires%20across%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20a%20major%20challenge%20emerged%3A%20fire%20hydrants%20in%20some%20areas%20ran%20dry%2C%20and%20low%20water%20pressure%20hampered%20efforts%20to%20contain%20the%20blaze.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flos-angeles-wildfire-la-wildfire-california-wildfire-explained-why-hydrants-ran-dry-during-deadly-los-angeles-wildfires-7448282%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%3A%20Getting%20praise%20from%20Hrithik%20felt%20like%20Oscar%20win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736573615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%