ination%20for%20tigers%20and%20spent%20four%20decades%20ensuring%20they%20were%20well%20protected.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821.jpg%20350w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fimg_0005_IMG0004-350x350-1-1735221821-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBilly%20Arjan%20Singh%20had%20a%20fascination%20for%20tigers%20and%20spent%20four%20decades%20ensuring%20they%20were%20well%20protected%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftigerhavensociety.org%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Haven%20Society%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20inception%20of%20Tiger%20Haven%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20how%20the%20summer%20of%201959%20was%20an%20unforgettable%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20out%20into%20the%20forest%20on%20Bhagwan%20Piari%2C%20the%20elephant%20with%20whom%20I%20spent%2025%20wonderful%20years.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20Himalayan%20ranges%20across%20the%20Dudhwa%20grasslands.%20At%20the%20confluence%20of%20the%20Soheli%20and%20Neora%20rivers%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20that%20was%20owned%20by%20a%20politician%20who%20had%20lost%20all%20interest%20in%20it.%20I%20bought%20it%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20functioning%20farm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%2C%20the%20farm%20went%20through%20a%20transmutation%20of%20sorts%20and%20became%20a%20haven%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279646%2Fbest-wildlife-photography-destinations-india-kaziranga-kabini-ranthambore-kaziranga%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20was%20allowed%20to%20thrive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20him%2C%20this%20act%20felt%20like%20%E2%80%9Clike%20repaying%20old%20debts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeconding%20this%20narrative%20of%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20tigers%20is%20Samir%20Sinha%20IFS%2C%20who%20shared%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20WWF-India%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20held%20very%20strong%20views%20and%20would%20regularly%20type%20away%20letters%20on%20his%20trusty%20typewriter%20to%20flag%20his%20concerns%20on%20issues%20that%20he%20considered%20important.%20Though%20his%20prolific%20writing%20was%20curtailed%20due%20to%20the%20physical%20effort%20of%20typing%20in%20his%20last%20years%2C%20even%20with%20failing%20health%2C%20his%20eyes%20would%20light%20up%20at%20the%20mention%20of%20the%20tiger%2C%20and%20he%20was%20always%20eager%20to%20engage%20in%20efforts%20in%20support%20of%20this%20majestic%20animal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20years%20succeeding%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20Dudhwa%20where%20he%20began%20his%20work%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiger%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20years%20were%20coloured%20with%20experiments%20and%20accolades%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20through%20waves%20of%20conflict%20posed%20by%20communities%20who%20depended%20on%20the%20game%20and%20stepping%20closer%20to%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%