jor%20challenge%20was%20their%20inexperience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20driven%20by%20willpower%2C%20but%20we%20had%20little%20experience%20and%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20skills.%20We%20realised%20that%20skills%20are%20developed%20through%20experience.%20So%2C%20we%20took%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20mentoring%20in%20areas%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20and%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20major%20challenge%20came%20when%20the%20trio%20encountered%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20fraud%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20taken%20a%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20loan%20to%20procure%20oil%20from%20farmers%2C%20and%20we%20received%20our%20first%20order%20in%20July%202022%2C%20a%20300-litre%20batch%20of%20cold-pressed%20oil.%20The%20order%20was%20valued%20around%20Rs%206-7%20lakh%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20send%20it%20to%20Noida%20in%20the%20NCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20all%20night%20packing%20and%20preparing%20the%20shipment%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20payment.%20The%20vendor%20told%20me%20that%20his%20bank%20account%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20working%20and%20that%20he%20could%20only%20transfer%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20initially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20troubles.%20The%20vendor%20ended%20up%20not%20paying%20the%20remaining%20Rs%204%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge.%20To%20repay%20the%20loan%2C%20we%20had%20to%20raise%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20difficulties%20but%20also%20being%20grateful%20for%20the%20support%20he%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3C