%2C%20the%20trio%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20never%20wavered.%20They%20knew%20that%20these%20challenges%20were%20part%20of%20the%20journey%20and%20continued%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20the%20support%20of%20their%20team%2C%20mentors%2C%20and%20the%20community%20they%20were%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeka%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363795%2Fnutmeg-export-from-india-farmers-pollachi-village-tamil-nadu-middlemen-fpc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevenue%20surged%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20in%202023-24%20to%20Rs%201.3%20crore%20in%20the%20first%20two%20quarters%20of%202024-25.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024-25%2C%20marking%20a%20more%20than%20fourfold%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20cold-pressed%20oils%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20320%20per%20litre%20for%20black%20mustard%2C%20Rs%20450%20for%20yellow%20mustard%2C%20and%20Rs%20500%20for%20groundnut%2C%20are%20gently%20extracted%20using%20the%20cold-press%20method%2C%20preserving%20their%20full%20nutritional%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Foreka%20plans%20to%20expand%20further%20by%20establishing%20processing%20units%20for%20five%20oilseeds%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20involving%2010%2C000%20farmers%2C%20and%20creating%20250%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20developing%20a%20%E2%80%98House%20of%20Mustard%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20project%20focused%20on%20value-added%20mustard%20products%20such%20as%20mustard%20sauce%20and%20chutney.%20Currently%20in%20the%20R%26amp%3BD%20stage%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20already%20produced%20samples%2C%20and%20the%20team%20is%20working%20to%20raise%20funds%20and%20develop%20a%20B2C%20branding%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20building%20livelihoods%2C%20not%20just%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20S