n%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Government%20Hospital.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20to%20retrieve%20blood%2C%20dress%20wounds%2C%20and%20identify%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Raghavan%20provided%20a%20monthly%20amount%20of%20Rs%20800%2C%20which%20was%20essential%20for%20my%20survival.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Raghavan%20also%20encouraged%20her%20to%20join%20the%20Community%20Action%20Network%20as%20an%20outreach%20worker.%20Despite%20her%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20HIV%2C%20Noori%20faced%20severe%20isolation%20and%20discrimination.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20pig%E2%80%99s%20fodder%20to%20eat%20as%20lunch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20a%20disheartening%20experience%20during%20an%20outreach%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20with%20HIV%20often%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hurdles.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stigma%20surrounding%20both%20my%20transgender%20identity%20and%20HIV%20status%20led%20many%20to%20fear%20and%20ostracise%20me%20and%20my%20friends%2C%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%2C%20who%20were%20also%20living%20with%20the%20virus.%20I%20hated%20it%20when%20doctors%2C%20who%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20disease%2C%20ill-treat%20their%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20treated%20us%20like%20dogs%2C%20throwing%20stones%20at%20us%2C%20thinking%20that%20it%20is%20transmitted%20like%20the%20flu%20virus.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20that%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Noori%20continued%20undeterred%2C%20raising%20awareness%20about%20HIV%20and%20advocating%20for%20the%20compassionate%20treatment%20of%20all%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20a