20aims%20to%20provide%20financial%20stability%20and%20foster%20agricultural%20growth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F394815%2Fcrop-insurance-schemes-india-2025-benefits-availability-pmfby-farmers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Daring%20Farming%20Methods%20Pushed%20Him%20From%20Daily%20Wage%20Worker%20to%20Padma%20Shri%20Winner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20childhood%20where%20the%20jungle%20was%20your%20playground%2C%20a%20world%20of%20endless%20wonder%20and%20danger.%20A%20world%20where%20farming%20was%20a%20distant%20dream%2C%20and%20survival%20depended%20on%20what%20the%20forest%20provided.%20This%20was%20the%20reality%20for%20young%20Sarbeswar%20Basumatary%2C%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20remote%20reaches%20of%20Chirang%20district%2C%20Assam.%20Today%2C%20at%2062%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20a%20survivor%2C%20but%20a%20trailblazer%2C%20earning%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20his%20revolutionary%20work%20in%20agriculture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20eight%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20five%20brothers%20and%20three%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%20life%20in%20Panbari%2C%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Chirang%20district%2C%20was%20difficult%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20His%20parents%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20labourers%20on%20construction%20sites%20and%20at%20landowners%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20did%20their%20best%20to%20care%20for%20their%20children%2C%20but%20resources%20were%20scarce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20we%20got%20lucky%2C%20they%20would%20find%20some%20work%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20we%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20goodwill%20of%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9COur%20village%20was%20a%20small%20settlement%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20forest.%20Because%20of%20the%20forest%20animals%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20cultivate%20any%20food%20for%20ourselves%3B%20as%20they%20would%20destroy%20the%20crops.%20We%20only%20had%20two%20choices%3A%20either%20become%20a%20labourer%20or%20head%20into%20the%20jungle%20to%20collect%20wild%20potatoes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20was%20no%20concept%20of%20a%20market%2C%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20to%20ask%20the%20landowners%20or%20wealthier%20people%20for%20rice%3B%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99d%20eat.%20I%20grew%20up%20eating%20that%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20learn%2C%20he%20overcame%20several%20challenges%20to%20attend%20night%20school%20but%20had%20to%20discontinue%20after%20class%205.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20survival%20had%20taken%20precedence%2C%20and%20Sarbeswar%20took%20up%20a%20job%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267799%2Fnit-karnataka-electric-bike-forest-surveillance-kudremukh-battery-range-specs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20forest%20guard%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20office%3B%20here%2C%20he%20spent%20about%20a%20year%2C%20taking%20care%20of%20poultry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201561px)%20100vw%2C%201561px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-20-at-8.42.33-AM_11zon-1734710658.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221561%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Papaya%20trees%20thrive%20in%20the%20jungle%2C%20showcasing%20integrated%20farming%20practices%20in%20Sarbeswar's%20fields.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%